    <string name="important_instructions_title">AMAKURU Y\'INGENZI</string>
    <string name="important_instructions">Inama ugirwa na AKILIMO zose zishingiye ku hantu uherereye, ingano y\'umurima wawe n\'ibiciro. Urugero, iyo ubuso bw\'umurima wawe wibeshye ukabugira bunini, bituma utanga igishoro kinini bityo ugahomba.  Ku rundi ruhande, niba ubuso bw\'umurima wawe ugereranije ari butoya ugereranije nukuri, ibi biganisha ku kudaha agaciro umusaruro wawe kandi ukaba watakaza amahirwe yo kubona inyungu mu murima wawe.</string>
